Name: Percentage of Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER out of all Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE

Metric: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' activities for cases where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' occurs

Name: Frequency of Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER in relation to total rejections

Name: Percentage of Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER followed by Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' out of all 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Percentage of Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER that lead to a new submission by the same employee within 30 days
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER by month to identify peak rejection periods
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'total', 'group_by': 'month'}

Name: Percentage of Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER from all activities performed by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' out of all cases

Name: Number of Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER with amounts above 100 euros
Metric: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' activities > 100 where ma is the last value of case:Amount

Name: Average number of days between Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER and Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for re-submission cases
Metric: the average of the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Percentage of Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER that are eventually approved after re-submission
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity LIKE 'Declaration APPROVED by %'"}

Name: Frequency of Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER in relation to total activities in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' out of all cases where '' does not happen

Metric: Number of 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' activities grouped by the last value of case:BudgetNumber

Name: Percentage of Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER that result in an appeal by the employee
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' out of all 'Declaration APPEAL by EMPLOYEE'
